room_title: Escape room "Alien Encounter" by The Escape Covington in Covington
room_address: 13433 Seymour Myers Blvd, Suite 4 Covington, LA 70433
room_description:
The year is 2060. The Earth has been invaded by an alien species known as the Voldran. As part of an elite research group aboard the starship Nuria, you have been tasked to travel to the outer reaches of space to locate the Voldran and discover their weakness.
But time is short, and resources are in limited supply. With just 60 minutes of oxygen remaining, you must you must navigate the inner depths of the Nuria and make your way to the control deck in order to make your escape. Earth has fallen, our leaders are dead, you are civilization's final hope.
